description: Put a fresh twist on the classic prawn cocktail with this sensational pasta salad complete with juicy tiger prawns, seafood sauce and creamy avocado.
keywords: Prawn salad,Prawn,Seafood,Video,Weeknight dinner,Low sugar,Nov 2021,Quick & easy dinner,High protein,High fibre,Christmas
name: Prawn Cocktail Salad Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 500g medium cooked tiger prawns, peeled, deveined, tails intact

recipeInstructions.text: Cook pasta in a saucepan of boiling, salted water according to packet instructions. Drain. Refresh under cold water. Drain.
Combine lemon juice, sauce and 1 tbs water in a small bowl.

Place pasta, cucumber, avocado, spinach, chives and half of the dill in a large bowl and toss to combine. Top with prawns and drizzle with dressing. Season with pepper. Scatter over remaining dill and serve with lemon wedges.
